      "content": "the problem is there is no \"pausing\" or \"resting\". it's not just a bad phase, it's just how my life is. it's a circle. no matter what I do, I end up exactly where I started, feeling just as empty and useless as before. it feels like the universe is just designed to keep me stuck.",
